<section id="approach" class="border-y border-border bg-surface-soft/60">
  <div class="container-full section-space">
    <div class="max-w-prose min-w-0">
      <p class="label-accent">Approach</p>
      <h2 class="mt-3 text-section-title text-balance">Start with the spend already committed.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 space-y-0" data-stages>
      <article class="stage-panel grid gap-8 py-10 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(220px,0.65fr)_minmax(0,1.35fr)] lg:gap-14" style="--i: 0">
        <div>
          <p class="stage-num">01 · Review</p>
          <h3 class="mt-3 text-2xl tracking-[-0.02em]">AI Value Recovery Review</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-[0.9375rem] font-semibold text-accent md:text-base">
            7–10 working days<br />From £2,500
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="min-w-0">
          <p class="text-lg leading-[1.65] text-ink">
            SignalFormation inventories current tools, projects and costs, then examines up to three
            important workflows with the people who use and own them.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-5 text-[0.9375rem] leading-[1.7] text-muted md:text-base">
            The review tests whether adoption, data, process design and operating ownership support a
            credible return. It also separates theoretical time savings from value the business can
            actually realise.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-8 grid gap-x-10 gap-y-6 border-t border-border pt-7 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Existing expenditure</h4>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-[1.6] text-muted">
                Licences, pilots, implementation fees, internal time and operating costs.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Workflow reality</h4>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-[1.6] text-muted">
                What remains manual, where outputs need checking and where rework appears.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Adoption and ownership</h4>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-[1.6] text-muted">
                Who uses the system, who owns the result and what blocks consistent use.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Operational value</h4>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-[1.6] text-muted">
                Changes to capacity, cost, conversion, quality, margin or risk.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 border-t border-border pt-7 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div>
              <p class="label">Included</p>
              <ul class="list-marked mt-3 space-y-2 text-[0.9375rem] leading-[1.65] text-muted">
                <li>Up to five stakeholder interviews</li>
                <li>Three workflow assessments</li>
                <li>Expenditure and ownership map</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="label">Delivered</p>
              <ul class="list-marked mt-3 space-y-2 text-[0.9375rem] leading-[1.65] text-muted">
                <li>Decision record for each initiative</li>
                <li>Prioritised 90-day action plan</li>
                <li>Executive findings session</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="stage-panel grid gap-8 border-t border-border py-10 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-12" style="--i: 1">
        <div>
          <p class="stage-num">02 · Remediate</p>
          <h3 class="mt-3 text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.02em]">Focused Remediation Sprint</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-[0.9375rem] font-semibold text-accent md:text-base">
